sequenceDiagram
    participant T as Score Event
    participant B as Backend
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    T->>B: Record score
    B->>DB: Insert skill score

    T->>B: Sync progress
    B->>DB: Fetch last 10 scores
    DB-->>B: Score window

    B->>B: Compute mean + std dev

    alt count < 3
        B->>B: trend = insufficient
    else count 3-5
        alt high deviation
            B->>B: trend = inconsistent
        else
            B->>B: trend = stable
        end
    else count >= 6
        alt high deviation
            B->>B: trend = inconsistent
        else
            B->>B: Compare recent vs older
        end
    end

    B->>DB: Upsert user_progress
